        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後爭持 恒指跌4點報23202點 小米再拖後腿 周大福成藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特普朗將於凌晨公布關稅決定，投資者普遍觀望，港股午後亦呈好淡爭持，小米(01810)則繼續拖大市後腿。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123039__source-web_01810-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123039__source-web_01810-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開39點後，初段反覆試底，一度失守23000點關口，低見22980點，跌225點，但未幾已收復二萬三，並於上午約10時15分過後開始轉升，早市中段最高曾見23393點，升186點，其後重現拾級下調走勢，午後轉好淡爭持，大部份時間報跌。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報23202點，跌4點或0.02%。恒生科技指數跑贏大市，收升19點或0.35%，報5426點；國企指數跌5點或0.07%，報8531點。主板成交2165.98億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14825164-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c4%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123202%e9%bb%9e-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e5%86%8d%e6%8b%96%e5%be%8c%e8%85%bf",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 16:20:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "據報中石化與寧德時代今年將建設最少500座換電站",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新華社報道指，中石化與寧德時代簽署產業與資本合作框架協議，今年將共同建設不少於500座換電站。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240311_FI_source-web_CATL.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20240311_FI_source-web_CATL.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，雙方未來致力於建設1萬座換電站。根據協議，中石化將與寧德時代全面深化長期戰略合作關係，共同構建全國換電網絡生態和標準建設，統一管理運營換電資產。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中石化目前已建成綜合加能站3萬座、易捷便利店2.8萬家、超充快充站逾萬座，全渠道用戶逾3億。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14825036-%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e4%b8%ad%e7%9f%b3%e5%8c%96%e8%88%87%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%b0%87%e5%bb%ba%e8%a8%ad%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%91500%e5%ba%a7%e6%8f%9b%e9%9b%bb%e7%ab%99-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9F%B3%E5%8C%963.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 16:05:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "天水圍栢慧豪園2房 443萬元成交  13年升值逾7成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產天水圍區域分行表示，栢慧豪園3月錄得12宗買賣成交，按月激增5倍。其中5座高層H室，實用面積494平方呎，兩房間隔，向東，業主趁單位租約完結沽貨止賺，開價468萬元，放盤不久獲買家洽購，減價25萬元，以443萬元沽出，實用呎價8968元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於2012年4月以255萬元買人單位，持貨13年，未計租金收入，賬面獲利188萬元，升值73%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14824368-%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%b4%e5%9c%8d%e6%a0%a2%e6%85%a7%e8%b1%aa%e5%9c%922%e6%88%bf-443%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-13%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc%e9%80%be7%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 15:25:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西營盤瑞華閣713實呎戶  同區用家意頭價888萬元連車位承接",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業西半山豪宅組天匯分行透露，該行剛促成西營盤瑞華閣一個713實呎戶成交，屋苑與港鐵出入口僅數分鐘步程，獲同區用家以888萬元連車位承接。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">位於西營盤高街100號瑞華閣，樓齡約49年，該成交的為高層B室單位，實用面積約為713呎，備有車位，加上屋苑位處名校網及旺中帶靜，獲同區用家垂青，並以888萬元成交，折合實用呎價約為12,454元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於1979年以約33萬元購入單位，並4萬元購入一個車位，共約37萬元，單位於2010年轉名，連車位以約150萬元成交，故實際上46年間物業連車位大幅升值約23倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14824363-%e8%a5%bf%e7%87%9f%e7%9b%a4%e7%91%9e%e8%8f%af%e9%96%a3713%e5%af%a6%e5%91%8e%e6%88%b6-%e5%90%8c%e5%8d%80%e7%94%a8%e5%ae%b6%e6%84%8f%e9%a0%ad%e5%83%b9888%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e9%80%a3%e8%bb%8a%e4%bd%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 15:26:01",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "屯門春和海景花園3房套戶連車位950萬成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">利嘉閣地產青山公路-滿名山分行促成屯門春和海景花園C座高層3室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約953方呎，屬3房1套連工人套房間隔，向東南，望海景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新買家為換樓客，業主原以1,080萬元放售，議價後以950萬元合理價成交，折合實用面積呎價約9,969元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，原業主於2012年以約648萬元買入單位，持貨至今轉手，帳面獲利約302萬元，期內物業升值近47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">屋苑現時有約3個單位放盤，最低入場費由約1,180萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14824353-%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e6%98%a5%e5%92%8c%e6%b5%b7%e6%99%af%e8%8a%b1%e5%9c%923%e6%88%bf%e5%a5%97%e6%88%b6%e9%80%a3%e8%bb%8a%e4%bd%8d950%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 15:26:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬深股市成交縮至少於萬億 股指收升不足0.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深兩市成交連續50個交易日破萬億的紀錄，終在今日中止，兩市股指在反覆微升下，交投縮至9744.93億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指低開4點後，雖然全日大部份時間均報升，但高位3361點時亦只升12點，午後但逐漸轉跌，曾觸及早市低位3343點；滬指最後收報3350點，升1點或0.05%，成交4116.66億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日走勢相若，由早市出現的全日高位10573點、升69點，到尾市全日低位10490點、跌12點，高低位相差僅82點；滬指收報10513點，升9點或0.09%，成交5628.27億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數則跌3點或0.08%，以3884點收市；創業板指數升2點或0.13%，報2104點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/光大銀行官網.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/光大銀行官網.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">各主要板塊跌多升少，銀行股表現較佳，尤其是中小型銀行，其中交通銀行(03328)A股(601328.SH)升2.29%，報7.58元；光大銀行(06818)A股(601818.SH)也升1.87%，報3.81元；青島銀行(03866)A股(002948.SZ)升1.68%，報4.23元；渝農商行(03618)A股(601077.SH)升1.49%，報6.13元；民生銀行(01988)A股(600016.SH)升1.52%，報4.01元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14824962-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e7%b8%ae%e8%87%b3%e5%b0%91%e6%96%bc%e8%90%ac%e5%84%84-%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87%e4%b8%8d%e8%b6%b30-1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-02 15:25:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
